title: nds4ios 1.0.ipa
description:
Play your favorite nds games on your iphone or ipad.

For Jailbroken iPhones

1. install appsync on iPhone

2. add IPA file to itunes

3. sync app to iphone or ipad



As Promised, I have now uploaded the most current version of the app. This contains the following features.

NDS4IOS 1.0
---------------------
Dropbox sync
Gamepad Controllers for IOS 7.0.0-7.1.2
